<glossary>
<definition id="fs-id1172099489735">
<term>internal energy</term>
<meaning id="fs-id1172099511850">average of the total mechanical energy of all the molecules or entities in the system</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-id1172101781722">
<term>quasi-static process</term>
<meaning id="fs-id1172099766500">evolution of a system that goes so slowly that the system involved is always in thermodynamic equilibrium</meaning>
</definition>
</glossary>
